query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND cct2.kind in ('cast','crew') AND cct1.kind in ('crew','complete','cast') AND it2.info not in ('LD group genre','LD audio quality','LD video artifacts','copyright holder','magazine cover photo','essays','quotes','LD picture format','admissions','LD number','screenplay-teleplay','birth name','studios','LD master format','book','votes','LD number of chapter stops','LD disc size','LD video quality','LD analog left') AND kt.kind not in ('video game','tv series','movie','tv mini series','video movie','tv movie') AND mi_idx.info > '8.0' AND (chn.name like '%John Wick%' OR chn.name like '%Tony Stark%' OR chn.name like '%Thor%' OR chn.name like '%Yoda%' OR chn.name like '%Iron Man%') AND (n.name like '%o%' OR n.name like '%T%' OR n.name like '%a%')
